            </div>
            <div class="right">
                <div class="information">
                    <h2 itemprop="headline">
                        <a href="https://www.gramophone.co.uk/features/article/dalia-stasevska-interview-our-tradition-is-exceptional-but-there-are-new-paths-to-explore">
                            Dalia Stasevska interview: ‘Our tradition is exceptional. But there are new paths to explore’
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    <ul class="details">
                                                        <li itemprop="datePublished" class="publish-date">
                                    Friday, April 19, 2024
                                </li>
                                                                                            </ul>
                        <p itemprop="abstract" class="excerpt">
                            From bridging genres to challenging cultural expectations, Dalia Stasevska is a conductor for our modern times
                        </p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
    <article itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Article" class="card article-block-medium">
        <div class=" contained">
            <div class="left">
                    <a href="https://www.gramophone.co.uk/blogs/article/exploring-schumann-s-chamber-music">
                                    <div class="image-resizer-container image-resized" data-responsive-image>
                <img data-src="/media/248296/the-o-fouchenneret.jpg?anchor=center&mode=resize&width=320&format=webp&quality=50" class="img-fluid" />
                <img min-width="320" class="img-fluid" data-src="/media/248296/the-o-fouchenneret.jpg?anchor=center&mode=resize&width=420&format=webp&quality=50" />
