            </div>

                    </a>
            </div>
            <div class="right">
                <div class="information">
                    <h2 itemprop="headline">
                        <a href="https://www.gramophone.co.uk/blogs/article/exploring-schumann-s-chamber-music">
                            Exploring Schumann&#39;s chamber music
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    <ul class="details">
                                                        <li itemprop="datePublished" class="publish-date">
                                    Tuesday, April 16, 2024
                                </li>
                                                                                            </ul>
                        <p itemprop="abstract" class="excerpt">
                            Pianist Th&#233;o Fouchenneret introduces two new recordings in the Schumann Collection: ‘Works With Wind Instruments’ and ‘Trios and Quartet For Piano and Strings (live)’
                        </p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
    <article itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Article" class="card article-block-medium">
        <div class=" contained">
            <div class="left">
                    <a href="https://www.gramophone.co.uk/features/article/top-20-haydn-recordings">
                                    <div class="image-resizer-container image-resized" data-responsive-image>
