                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    <ul class="details">
                                                        <li itemprop="datePublished" class="publish-date">
                                    Tuesday, April 16, 2024
                                </li>
                                                                                            </ul>
                        <p itemprop="abstract" class="excerpt">
                            Twenty outstanding Verdi recordings, featuring Ren&#233; Jacobs, Claudio Abbado, Nikolaus Harnoncourt, Alison Balsom, Alfred Brendel and many more
                        </p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>

